data.description: Wonderful mid-century home available now for viewings! Stunning entry and living room spaces with wall full of windows. Stone fireplace, beam ceilings, and wood floors are other cozy additions to the living room. Kitchen features modern tile flooring, stainless appliances, and eat-in dining space. Bedrooms are all great size with all but one having wood floors. Primary bedroom has sliding doors and patio leading to the spacious backyard. Large shed in backyard for storage, plus attached one car garage. New windows during current ownership/last five years as well. Schedule your appointment today!
